      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal equivalency analysis between validation and intended use input parameters is not required beyond qualitative documentation.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative documentation of the mapping between validation experimental inputs and intended use model inputs is provided in the simulation protocol. Formal equivalency quantification is not required at MRL 2."
    }
